Title: WebDAV PROPFIND Extension To List Specified Namespaces Author(s): J. Stracke Filename: draft-ietf-webdav-propfind-space-00.txt 
Pages: 6 Date: 16-Sep-99 This document specifies an extension to the [WEBDAV] PROPFIND method to permit a WebDAV client to request all properties which belong to a specified namespace or namespaces. 
